    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a superlative example of the E46 platform, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with documented rod bearing replacement and professional subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original rigidity, benefitting from a complete suspension refresh using OEM components to preserve the legendary M-division turn-in and feedback. Finished in pristine Laguna Seca Blue, this vehicle has been maintained to a concours standard, free of common pixel degradation or interior trim wear. A turnkey, collector-grade machine for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
